-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tema-pesni/privlekatelnyy-paren&quot;&gt;Привлекательный парень&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Теги:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/vsyo-ravno-lyublyu&quot;&gt;всё равно люблю&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/lyublyu-ego&quot;&gt;люблю его&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-chuvstva field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Чувства:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/blazhenstvo&quot;&gt;Блаженство&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/blizost&quot;&gt;Близость&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/vina&quot;&gt;Вина&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/vlechenie&quot;&gt;Влечение&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/lyubov&quot;&gt;Любовь&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/otkrovenie&quot;&gt;Откровение&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/otreshyonnost&quot;&gt;Отрешённость&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/priznatelnost&quot;&gt;Признательность&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
